snippet.title: Puyo Puyo Quest Arcade (PV)
snippet.description: Puyo Puyo Quest Arcade is a RPG puzzle game by Sega. The game will be out in 2013. It's an arcade adaptation of Puyo Puyo Quest for iOS mobile phones.
